## Design System Rules (Enforced Across All Phases)

| Rule | Enforcement |
|---|---|
| All colors from `design-tokens.css` | No hex values, no Tailwind color utilities |
| Typography from design tokens | Roboto, font sizes in rem, clamp for display text |
| Semantic color roles | `--color-primary`, `--color-surface`, `--color-error`, etc. |
| Empty states on all data pages | Title + explanation + CTA button |
| Loading states on async ops | Skeleton loaders, submit button spinners |
| Notifications | Toast system (success/error/warning), auto-dismiss |
| Forms | Labels, required markers, server-side validation, error below field |
| Tables | Pagination, status badges, search/filter, empty states |
| Naming | Files: kebab-case, Components: PascalCase, Functions: camelCase |

